    question: "What's not covered by legal protection insurance?",
    answer: "Common exclusions include business/commercial legal matters (unless specifically covered), family law disputes like divorce, intentional criminal acts, tax evasion cases, and legal issues that existed before the policy started. Each policy has specific exclusions that should be reviewed carefully."
  }
];
---

<Layout
  title="Legal Protection Insurance Switzerland: Complete Guide 2025"
  description="Comprehensive legal protection insurance in Switzerland. Navigate complex legal situations with expert coverage. Compare providers and understand your options for complete legal security."
  image="https://res.cloudinary.com/dphbnwjtx/image/upload/v1747314246/a-sketch-illustration-of-a-rugged-black-_hUCr82DTTTuXAOEvaqa8Kg_m4byvbySR62_wC1A_8p51A_hgfeoe.webp"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
